---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service - Domain Discoverer" description="Simple terms that explain how you may use this website and what you can expect from us.">
  <section class="container-pad">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">Please read these terms carefully. By using DomainDiscoverer.com you agree to them.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-8 mb-2">Purpose of the Site</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We provide information and tools that help people discover valuable domain names. Content is educational. It is not legal, financial, or investment advice.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Acceptable Use</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-white/80 max-w-3xl space-y-1">
      <li>Do not attempt to disrupt the site or its services</li>
      <li>Do not scrape or copy content at scale</li>
      <li>Do not use automated queries that overload our endpoints</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Accounts and Email</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">If you subscribe to our newsletter you must provide a valid email address. You can unsubscribe at any time. We only email people who opt in.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Links and Affiliates</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We link to third party tools and registrars. Some links may be affiliate links. We do not control third party services and are not responsible for their content or policies.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">All content on this site is owned by Domain Discoverer or its content providers. You may link to our pages and share short excerpts with credit.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">No Warranties</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We aim for accuracy but provide content as is. We do not guarantee outcomes or the availability of any domain name.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We are not liable for indirect or consequential damages that arise from using this site or relying on its content.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Changes</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">We may update these terms. The latest version is posted on this page. If changes are important, we will note that clearly.</p>

    <h2 class="font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">Questions about these terms can be sent via our <a class="underline" href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

